    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? Because this beauty is absolutely stunning! I've babied this car from day one, and it's in truly incredible shape\u2014not a scratch or a speck of dust to be found. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh, new-car smell that everyone loves. I'm honestly so sad to see it go, but I'm looking for a great new home for it. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
