    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. The powertrain is in superlative mechanical order, having undergone a comprehensive rod bearing service and VANOS overhaul to ensure long-term reliability. The 6-speed manual transmission offers precise shift gates, feeding power to the rear wheels via a variable M-differential lock. Structural integrity is paramount; the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to mitigate common chassis fatigue. With factory-spec suspension geometry and a flawless exterior finish, this vehicle offers a pure, unfiltered driving experience for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
